<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="0991-08-10"><a href="/wiki/August_10" title="August 10">10 August</a> <a href="/wiki/991" title="991">991</a></span></td>
<td>approximately 200 Anglo-Saxons</td>
<td>2,000-4,000 Vikings</td>
<td>1:10 to 1:20</td>
<td>A handful of Anglo-Saxon warriors led by <a href="/wiki/Byrhtnoth" title="Byrhtnoth">Byrhtnoth</a> fought and were eventually overwhelmed by a force of 2,000 - 4,000 <a href="/wiki/Vikings" title="Vikings" class="mw-redirect">Vikings</a>.</td>
