<td><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Blood_River" title="Battle of Blood River">Battle of Blood River</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1838-12-16"><a href="/wiki/December_16" title="December 16">16 December</a> <a href="/wiki/1838" title="1838">1838</a></span></td>
<td>470 Voortrekkers defenders</td>
<td>10,000-20,000 Zulu attackers</td>
<td>1:21 to 1:43</td>
<td>470 Boer <a href="/wiki/Voortrekkers" title="Voortrekkers">Voortrekkers</a> successfully defended an impromptu <a href="/wiki/Laager" title="Laager" class="mw-redirect">laager</a> of wagons against 10,000 <a href="/wiki/Zulus" title="Zulus" class="mw-redirect">Zulus</a>.</td>
