<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1847-09-13"><a href="/wiki/September_13" title="September 13">13 September</a> <a href="/wiki/1847" title="1847">1847</a></span></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Ni%C3%B1os_H%C3%A9roes" title="Niños Héroes">Niños Héroes</a> - Six Mexican cadets fought to the last man, after <a href="/wiki/Nicol%C3%A1s_Bravo" title="Nicolás Bravo">General Bravo</a> ordered them to fall back during the <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Chapultepec" title="Battle of Chapultepec">Siege of Chapultepec</a>; one of the last events of the <a href="/wiki/Mexican-American_War" title="Mexican-American War" class="mw-redirect">Mexican-American War</a></td>
