<td><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Tirad_Pass" title="Battle of Tirad Pass">Battle of Tirad Pass</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1899-12-02"><a href="/wiki/December_2" title="December 2">2 December</a> <a href="/wiki/1899" title="1899">1899</a></span></td>
<td>60 Filipino troops</td>
<td>500 American soldiers</td>
<td>1:8</td>
<td>The stand of 60 Filipino soldiers under General <a href="/wiki/Gregorio_del_Pilar" title="Gregorio del Pilar">Gregorio del Pilar</a> covered the retreat of <a href="/wiki/President" title="President">President</a> <a href="/wiki/Emilio_Aguinaldo" title="Emilio Aguinaldo">Emilio Aguinaldo</a> during the <a href="/wiki/Philippine-American_War" title="Philippine-American War">Philippine-American War</a>.</td>
