<td><a href="/wiki/Lost_Battalion_(World_War_I)" title="Lost Battalion (World War I)">Lost Battalion</a></td>
<td>2 – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1918-10-07"><a href="/wiki/October_7" title="October 7">7 October</a> <a href="/wiki/1918" title="1918">1918</a></span></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td>An American battalion under Major <a href="/wiki/Charles_White_Whittlesey" title="Charles White Whittlesey">Charles White Whittlesey</a> held out in the Argonne Forrest.</td>
