<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Zadw%C3%B3rze" title="Battle of Zadwórze">Battle of Zadwórze</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1920-08-17"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="08-17"><a href="/wiki/August_17" title="August 17">August 17</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1920" title="1920">1920</a></span></td>
<td>330 mostly ill-equipped <a href="/wiki/Poland" title="Poland">Polish</a> irregulars</td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Bolshevik" title="Bolshevik">Bolshevik</a> <a href="/wiki/1st_Cavalry_Army" title="1st Cavalry Army" class="mw-redirect">1st Cavalry Army</a></td>
<td></td>
<td>The result is a Russian tactical victory, but a Polish strategic victory. The Polish force, although inflicting heavy losses, was almost completely annihilated. Their stand did manage to halt the Soviet advance and prevent the Bolsheviks from seizing Lwów, effectively buying time for the Polish defense of Warsaw.</td>
