<td>414 Chinese soldiers of 524th Regiment, <a href="/wiki/88th_Division" title="88th Division">88th Division</a>, <a href="/wiki/National_Revolutionary_Army" title="National Revolutionary Army">National Revolutionary Army</a></td>
