<td></td>
<td></td>
<td>Defense of the <a href="/wiki/Soviet_Union" title="Soviet Union">Soviet</a> 316th Rifle Division under command of General <a href="/wiki/Ivan_Panfilov" title="Ivan Panfilov">Ivan Panfilov</a> at <a href="/w/index.php?title=Dubosekovo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Dubosekovo (page does not exist)">Dubosekovo</a> near <a href="/wiki/Volokolamsk" title="Volokolamsk">Volokolamsk</a> during the Battle of Moscow.</td>
