<td><a href="/wiki/Battle_for_Berlin" title="Battle for Berlin" class="mw-redirect">Battle for Berlin</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="04-16"><a href="/wiki/April_16" title="April 16">16 April</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1945-05-08"><a href="/wiki/May_8" title="May 8">8 May</a> <a href="/wiki/1945" title="1945">1945</a></span></td>
