<td><a href="/wiki/Bukit_Kepong_Incident" title="Bukit Kepong Incident">Bukit Kepong Incident</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1950-02-23"><a href="/wiki/February_23" title="February 23">23 February</a> <a href="/wiki/1950" title="1950">1950</a></span></td>
<td>25 police and auxiliary police personnel</td>
<td>200 Communists</td>
<td>1:8</td>
<td>A police station near <a href="/wiki/Muar" title="Muar">Muar</a>, <a href="/wiki/Malaysia" title="Malaysia">Malaysia</a> was besieged by Communist guerrillas.</td>
