<td><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Dien_Bien_Phu" title="Battle of Dien Bien Phu">Battle of Dien Bien Phu</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="03-13"><a href="/wiki/March_13" title="March 13">13 March</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1954-05-07"><a href="/wiki/May_7" title="May 7">7 May</a> <a href="/wiki/1954" title="1954">1954</a></span></td>
<td>10,800 French</td>
<td>63,000 Vietnamese</td>
<td>1:5</td>
<td>The final battle of the <a href="/wiki/First_Indochina_War" title="First Indochina War">First Indochina War</a> pitted <a href="/wiki/French_Union" title="French Union">French Union</a> forces against <a href="/wiki/Viet_Minh" title="Viet Minh">Viet Minh</a> forces under General <a href="/wiki/Vo_Nguyen_Giap" title="Vo Nguyen Giap" class="mw-redirect">Vo Nguyen Giap</a>.</td>
