<td><a href="/wiki/Rezang_La" title="Rezang La">Battle of Rezang La/Chushul</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1962-11-18"><a href="/wiki/November_18" title="November 18">18 November</a> <a href="/wiki/1962" title="1962">1962</a></span></td>
<td>123 Indian soldiers from <a href="/wiki/Kumaon_Regiment" title="Kumaon Regiment">Kumaon Regiment</a> of <a href="/wiki/Indian_Army" title="Indian Army">Indian Army</a></td>
<td>Approx. 7000 Chinese soldiers</td>
<td>1:57</td>
<td>The 13th Battalion, <a href="/wiki/Kumaon_Regiment" title="Kumaon Regiment">Kumaon Regiment</a> led by <a href="/wiki/Shaitan_Singh" title="Shaitan Singh">Shaitan Singh</a> at Rezang La (<i><a href="/wiki/Sino-Indian_War" title="Sino-Indian War">Sino-Indian War</a></i>). Of the 123 Indian soldiers, 109 died.</td>
