<tr>
<td>Landing Zone (LZ) X-Ray in the <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Ia_Drang" title="Battle of Ia Drang">Battle of Ia Drang</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="11-14"><a href="/wiki/November_14" title="November 14">14 November</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1965-11-17"><a href="/wiki/November_17" title="November 17">17 November</a> <a href="/wiki/1965" title="1965">1965</a></span></td>
<td>1000 American Soldiers</td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Vietnam_People%27s_Army" title="Vietnam People's Army">Vietnam People's Army</a> (Peoples' Army of Vietnam, North Vietnamese Army) (4000)</td>
<td>1:4</td>
<td>The 1st Battalion/<a href="/wiki/7th_Cavalry" title="7th Cavalry" class="mw-redirect">7th Cavalry</a>, the 2nd Battalion/7th Cavalry, and the 1st Battalion/<a href="/wiki/5th_Cavalry" title="5th Cavalry" class="mw-redirect">5th Cavalry</a> at the Battle of Ia Drang. Depicted in the film <a href="/wiki/We_Were_Soldiers" title="We Were Soldiers">We Were Soldiers</a>.</td>
