<td><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Longewala" title="Battle of Longewala">Battle of Longewala</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="12-05"><a href="/wiki/December_5" title="December 5">5 December</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1971-12-06"><a href="/wiki/December_6" title="December 6">6 December</a> <a href="/wiki/1971" title="1971">1971</a></span></td>
<td>1 Indian Company (120)</td>
<td>1 Pakistani Armoured Brigade (3,000)</td>
<td>1:25</td>
<td>The Indian 'A' company of 120 odd soldiers of the 23rd Battalion, Punjab Regiment, managed to hold a 2,000-3,000 strong assault force of the 51st Infantry Brigade of the Pakistani Army, backed by the 22nd Armoured Regiment, before the Indian Air Force flew in.</td>
