<td>The <a href="/wiki/Barak_Armored_Brigade" title="Barak Armored Brigade">Barak Armored Brigade</a> defending the southern <a href="/wiki/Golan_Heights" title="Golan Heights">Golan Heights</a> during the <a href="/wiki/Yom_Kippur_War" title="Yom Kippur War">Yom Kippur War</a>.</td>
