<td>April 1975</td>
<td>6,000 ARVN soldiers</td>
<td>40,000 North Vietnamese</td>
<td>1:7</td>
<td>During last major battle of the <a href="/wiki/Vietnam_War" title="Vietnam War">Vietnam War</a>, the <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Xuan_Loc" title="Battle of Xuan Loc" class="mw-redirect">Battle of Xuan Loc</a>, the vastly outnumbered <a href="/wiki/ARVN_18th_Division" title="ARVN 18th Division" class="mw-redirect">ARVN 18th Division</a> stood and fought at Xuan Loc.</td>
