<td colspan="6" style="border-top:1px solid #cee0f2;"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Hill_776" title="Battle of Hill 776" class="mw-redirect">Battle of Hill 776</a></td>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="02-29"><a href="/wiki/February_29" title="February 29">29 February</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2000-03-01"><a href="/wiki/March_1" title="March 1">1 March</a> <a href="/wiki/2000" title="2000">2000</a></span></td>
<td>85 <a href="/wiki/VDV" title="VDV">Russian paratroopers</a></td>
<td>~2,000 Chechen <a href="/wiki/Mujahideen" title="Mujahideen">mujahideen</a><sup class="noprint Template-Fact"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources&#160;since October 2007" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed">citation needed</a></i>]</span></sup><sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span title="The material in the vicinity of this tag may not be factual or accurate&#160;from December 2008" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Disputed_statement" title="Wikipedia:Disputed statement">dubious</a> <span class="metadata">– <a href="/wiki/Talk:Last_stand#Dubious" title="Talk:Last stand">discuss</a></span></i>]</span></sup></td>
<td>~1:24</td>
<td>During one of the last major battles of the <a href="/wiki/Second_Chechen_War" title="Second Chechen War">Second Chechen War</a>, a vastly outnumbered company of Russian airborne troops stood and fought against an assault by Chechen rebels on Hill 776 near Ulus-Kert in the <a href="/wiki/Chechen_Republic" title="Chechen Republic" class="mw-redirect">Chechen Republic</a>. All but one of the 85 Russians died - 400 rebels were killed.<sup class="noprint Template-Fact"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources&#160;since October 2007" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed">citation needed</a></i>]</span></sup><sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span title="The material in the vicinity of this tag may not be factual or accurate&#160;from December 2008" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Disputed_statement" title="Wikipedia:Disputed statement">dubious</a> <span class="metadata">– <a href="/wiki/Talk:Last_stand#Dubious" title="Talk:Last stand">discuss</a></span></i>]</span></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="6" style="border-top:1px solid #cee0f2;"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
